  <md:title>SSPD_Chapter 1_Part8_AppendixXXXIV_Travelling Waves</md:title>
  <md:abstract>Appendix XXXIV refers to SSPD_Chapter_Part8 It gives a simple quantitative method of arriving at the solution of Wave Equations of Electro-Magnetic Field Theory. We have a similar methodology of arriving at the solution of Schrodinger Equation.</md:abstract>
